https://docs.continuum.io/anaconda-cloud/using#Packages
http://pythonvision.org/basic-tutorial/

1x:
conda install anaconda-client anaconda-build
conda config --add channels sweetser

Per project...

download package.tar.gz
uppack
cd package

build it:
python setup.py sdist

upload:
anaconda upload dist/package-1.4.1.tar.gz

pip install:
pip install --extra-index-url https://pypi.anaconda.org/sweetser/package package

